&lt;p>DevOps, short for Development and Operations, is a set of practices, principles, and cultural philosophies that aim to improve collaboration and efficiency between software development teams and IT operations teams. It emphasizes the integration of software development and IT operations, breaking down traditional silos and fostering a collaborative approach throughout the entire software delivery lifecycle.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>